4. MITIGATIONS
‚Äã‚ÄãMitsubishi Electric recommends customers take the following mitigation measures to minimize the risk of an attacker exploiting this vulnerability:

‚ÄãUse a firewall or virtual private network (VPN), etc., to prevent unauthorized access when internet access is required.
‚ÄãUse within a LAN and block access from untrusted networks and hosts through firewalls.
‚ÄãRestrict physical access to affected products and the LAN they connect.

